README for Bombilla
Author/Contact: Philip Levis <pal@cs.berkeley.edu>

Description:

Bombilla is a test application for Mate, a system for programming
sensor networks in high-level application specific scripts.
Installing this application on a mote will install Bombilla,
which has two event handlers. A more detailed presentation of Mate can
be found in the manual contained in tinyos-1.x/doc.

Tools:

net.tinyos.script.Scripter

This class, *when executed from this directory*, will load a scripting
interface to the Bombilla VM.

